          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A tapping practice from Day 15 of the SLEEP program. The session has two rounds: one to do during the day (releasing the pattern that equates stress with productivity) and one for the evening (actively signalling the body to downshift). Use both, or just the evening round if you're coming to this at bedtime."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          { "type": "text", "text": "New to tapping? Read " },
